Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:18.74,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Even though it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.95,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…even though I feel sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:29.28,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…in the court I feel just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:37.48,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,When I hear the ball flying, my heart races.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:41.56,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Receive. Toss. Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:46.55,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,One-two, one-two! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:49.35,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,But sometimes I cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:52.41,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,I'm a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:01:00.68,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Through the tears and sweat, putting up a youthful fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:08.82,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…under the blue sky, I just want to scream:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:16.98,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:26.12,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{涙に映える夕陽}Episode 011\NTears sparkling in sunrise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとうございました。}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいわ。}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり来たわね。}They did come after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{一緒にいたのは東海中学のバレー部よ。}She brought the girls from Toukai's volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{元浜紀中四天王の泉さんはあたしたちに一体何の話があるって言うの？}What does the former member of Hamaki's Big Four want from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{早く言って。}Please tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{それもあたしたちのバレー部のためになる話Xなんて何なの？}What was this talk important for our club?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{実は…}Actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{明日の地区予選の決勝戦ね…是非あんたたちに勝ってもらいたいと思って－}I want you to win the tomorrow's district qualifiers—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{何ですって？}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{本気なの？}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{酷い。}That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{許せないわ。}I won't forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{知ってる?}Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしバレー部を辞めたのよ。}I quit the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは聞いてたわ。}We heard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうして辞めたんだろうと思ってたなのよ。}I wondered why you quit the club myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね？}You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしだって辞めたくなかったわ。}To be honest, I didn't really want to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、富士見学園のバレー部は合併したあたしたちは邪魔だったのね。}But when we merged with Fujimi Academy, their team saw us as a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{それでキャプテンをしていたあたしを追い出そうと企てたのよ。}They conspired to drive me, a captain, out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{酷いでしょう？}Cruel, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは酷い目に遭ったわ。}It felt terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{思い出しでも悔しくて。}Just remembering it is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当に涙が出るわ。}I ended up in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん…}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かるわ、気持ち。}You have my sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{それで？}What happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{その張本人は鮎原こずえと早川みどりなの。}The originators were Ayuhara Kozue and Hayakawa Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{二人は富士見学園バレー部を自分たちだけのものにしておきたいのよ。}These two want to keep Fujimi Academy's volleyball club to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。何てこと！}What a thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{しい！}Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{静に。}Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし一人で我慢て済むことは、そうするわ。}If this concerned only me, I'd endure it in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、でもさ…}But… but…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう言う人達が地区代表として、全日本の大会に(XXX・必定する)ことはどうしても許せないのよ。}I can't allow such people to be elected in the district qualifiers and proceed to the All-Japan Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。そうだわ。}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーを自分達だけのものにしようなんて…}Trying to seize the club for oneself is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{だから…}That's my reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{あしたの決勝戦を是非あんたたちに勝ってもらいたいのよ。}That's why I'd like you to win the tomorrow's match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{それでね…}To ensure it…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見学園の作戦とメンバーを欠点を教えるわね。}…I will tell you the Fujimi's strategy and members' weak points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{この六人はレギュラーメンバーよ。}These six are their regular members.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原と早川と二人は決定的にマークすること。いい？}By all means, you need to mark both Ayuhara and Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{香取は(XX・前方のはうまいけど…}Katori's aim is precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・左右)は弱いわ。}But she's weak with side attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{得に左をつけば絶対よ。}Her right side is particularly bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{それから、工藤はね…}Moving on to Kudou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんて卑怯な。}How low!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくらあたしたちを勝たしたくないから、一緒にやってきたチームメイトまで裏切るなんて…}No matter how much she wants to see us fail, betraying her friends is unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうする？}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{やる？}Do we stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{今彼女取っちめりより、先ず明日の決勝戦に勝つことよ。}Rather than taking them on now, we should focus on the tomorrow's match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか。}We won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…苦しい。}Ah, how frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいぞ。XXX。}Good going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張れ！}Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:05:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{又も、キャプテン鮎原こずえのスパイクが見事決まりました。}Yet another captain Ayuhara Kozue's splendid spike hits the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{全日本女子中学バレー部をXXXは予選の決勝に来て、富士見学園の猛攻が爆発XXX漢字で。}Having advanced to the All-Japan's final district qualifying match, Fujimi Academy continues to attack fiercely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいぞ！}Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{昨日の曽根中学との大戦で、あれほどXXX富士見学園とは思うありません。}Today's Fujimi's power cannot be compared with yesterday's match with Sone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{あい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほらほら、何よ。}What are you doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{ワアアイ！}Waai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って！}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいぞ、鮎原さん！}Good going, Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{その調子だ！}Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張れぇぇえ！}Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたXか。}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{作戦を変えた。}The strategy was changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{丸でこっちの計画をXXX。}It's almost as if they figured out my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{それにしても、鮎原こずえは強いわ。}At any rate, Ayuhara Kozue sure is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{だからあたしはあんたを憎いんだ。}That's why I hate you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・なのついたではね)裏をかかれてさ。}Looks like shuffling the attacks paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{このままでいただきね。}At this rate we've already won.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{開いても全日本の大会出るために必死よ。}The opponent has trained for All-Japan games too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXけないわ。}Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、一体どうなっただろう?}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{話とでは全然違うじゃないの。}That's not what she promised to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{メンバーも変わってるし、作戦は全然治が上。}They went with different players. The strategy's wrong too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは騙されたのよ。}We have been tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{可笑しいと思ったわ。}I thought it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{自分の学校を裏切る人なんかいないのよ。}No one would betray their school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{悔しいけど真に受けたあたしたちは馬鹿だったのよ。}It's painful, but we're fools for having believed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう遅いわ。}It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{後ワンポイントでお終いよ。}Just one point left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{最後まで頑張るわ。}Let's try until end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{もうそれしかないわ。}We can't do much else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、行こう。}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー行きましょう。\Nー頑張ってね。}- Let's do this!\N- Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと！}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Xよ！}Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどり！}Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{ワアアイ！}Waai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{ヤホオ！}Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{勝ったわ、勝ったわ！}We won, we won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{よかった！}I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー先生！\Nー先生！}- Professor!\N- Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆！よく頑張った。}All of you! You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、いいか。今日勝ったといっても、地区予選の代表に成ったXだ。}With today's victory, we became our district's representatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{お前たち。地区代表ぐらいXXないぞ。}This doesn't mean you can take it easy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{全国大会まで後一週間。}One week until the All-Japan Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{その時には、全国からXXの代表が集まる。}The participants will be the best schools in the whole country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当に苦しい試合がこれからX。}The truly difficult games are yet ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{それを忘れない。}Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー分かったな？\Nーはい。}- Got it?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーはい。\Nーはい。}- Yeah.\N- Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーおめでとう！\Nーおめでとう！}- Congratulations!\N- Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{よかったわね。}You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{よかった！}I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{おめでとう！}Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{これで全国大会必定だね。}You made it to the All-Japan Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんは一緒じゃなかったの？}Weren't you together with Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？お…}Eh? Err…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{どこへ行ったかな。}I wonder where she went to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{確かに、来ただようだったけど。}I think I saw her come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{来られるわけがないでしょう？}There's no way she'd come, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？どう言う意味だ？}Eh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、泉さんはあたしたちが負ければいいと思ってるんだから。}You see, Izumi-san thinks we should lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなことはないさ。泉くんは人じゃないんだ。}It can't be. Izumi-kun is not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くんは…}Izumi-kun is—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいのよ、もう。}Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さん、聞きたくないわ。}Tsutomu-san, I don't want to listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの人はね、どんな人か、はっきり分かったんだから。}We had a chance to see what this person is truly like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、こずえさん？}Right, Kozue-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{君達…}Girls…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体何のようがあるだ、こんな所で?}What in the world are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう少し待ってて。}Please be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さんに見せたいものがあるだから。}We want to show you something, Tsutomu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{来た！}She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{来たわよ。}She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほ？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん！}Izumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんは一体どんな人か、見せてあげるわ。}We'll show you what kind of person Izumi-san is really like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん。}Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{は？}Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん。今日の試合見てくれた？}Izumi-san. Did you see our match today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{負ければいいと思って、あたしたちが軽く勝ったので、あなたがっかりしてるんでしょう。}You wanted us to lose and here we are, having won by a landslide. Disappointed, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{笑えせないでよ。}Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日勝ったことそんなにあたしに自慢したいの？}Do you really want to boast to me this badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{それでこんな所であたしを待ち伏せていたのね。}You even came to ambush me in such a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうなの？}That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{それにさ。}Furthermore…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{勝ったと言っても、XXXじゃない？}Even if you won, what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{全国大会でまた今日のようにうまく行くと思ったら、とんでもない間違いよ。}If you think the tournament will be as easy as today, you're terribly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう？}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなにあたしたちを負けたXいの？}Wanna see us lose so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたちの勝とうや負けようか、あたしには全然関係のないことよ。}Whether you win or lose doesn't concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはもうバレー部員じゃないんですから。そうでしょう？}I'm not in your club anymore. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{惚けないでよ！}Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、何のこと？}Ah, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{どこまで惚けるつもりなの？}How long will you drag this farce?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{涼しいわね。}This is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{スパイのまでなんかしたのは一体どこのだれなの?}Who did you spy for and for how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{スパイ？}Spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{変な言い掛かりよしてよ。}Don't make accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん、昨日あたしたちはあなたと同じ喫茶店にいたのよ。}Izumi-san. We went to the same coffee shop yesterday as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたが東海中学のバレー部の人達と話してる時に。}We saw you meet girls from the Toukai's volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部員だったあなたが富士見学園チームの作戦や決定を試合の相手に知らせるなんて…}You told them the Fujimi Academy team's strategy and the members' weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{これは一体どう言うことなの？}What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん。}Izumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{きみ、今の話は本当なのか？}What they just said is true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{何とか言ったらどうなのよ?}How about you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん、あたしたちXXXバレー部から追い出したりしたの？}Izumi-san, did you forget our time together in the volleyball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{それに、あたしたちのことばかりじゃないわ。}And not only ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:11:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{同じ仲間だった、工藤さんや香取さんが、このこと聞いたら、何と思うかしら？}What if your friends, what if Kudou-san, Katori-san heard us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆XXXバレーボールがXXX優勝するためにどれだけ一所懸命努力してるか？}How much effort did every one of us put into that club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたはよく知ってるじゃないの。}You know it very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんな卑怯なこと…恥ずかしくないの？}Aren't you ashamed of your actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちに負けたことはそんなに悔しいの？}Did losing to us hurt you so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{だったら…だったらバレーでもつかってくればいいじゃないの？}Then why… why don't we settle it through volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちと一緒に…あたしたちと一緒にバレーをやってあたしたちを任すぐらい強く成ればいいじゃないの？}Why don't we work together? Why don't we play volleyball together and form a strong team?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん。}Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしてそんなことをしたんだ？}Why did you do such thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{放っといてよ。}Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしだって辞めたって、辞めたいじゃないわ。}Even though I quit, I didn't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{それほど続けたかったか。}But I went through it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さん、よく知ってるじゃないの。}Tsutomu-san, you know it the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは分かっているさ。}I understand that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、だからと言って、そんなことをしてもいいと言うことには…}But this doesn't mean it justifies what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かってないわ。}You don't understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん。}Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:11:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん！}Izumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{だれにもあたしのことなんか分からないわ。}No one understands me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん！}Izumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さん。}Tsutomu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体どうしたて言うの？}What did she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんに何があったの？}Did something happen to Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くんはバレー部を辞めたらは君達に負けた所為じゃないんだ。}Izumi-kun didn't quit because she has lost to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{いや、もちろん…そのショックも少しXったけど…}Well, the shock from it surely played some part.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{実は、手首の具合が悪くて自分の思うように重くなかったんだ。}But the main reason is that she can't bend her wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{手首？}The wrist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{手が…}My hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{痛い。}It hurts…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、あの時ボールが手首に当たったのは…}So she must've hurt it around that time when she hit the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{や、前から時々具合が悪かったんだよ。}Nah, it was aching from time to time even before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{医者は言うにはなんでも見に手首をXX使いすぎだXXってね。}The doctor said she put too much stress on her wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。そうだったの。}Ah. That's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{医者にバレーボールは絶対に休むようにって言われたんでそうだ。}I heard the doctor ordered her to take a break from the volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{だけど、泉くんはね…}But instead, Izumi-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。痛い。}Ah… it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり…}Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{又やってるの？}Are you playing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{止めなさいX分からないの？}You shouldn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{お医者さんにXでしょう。}The doctor has said it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{半年ぐらいは絶対にバレーをやってらいけませんって。}He ordered you to take a break from the volleyball for half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{止めなさい！}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは又キャプテンとしてバレー部に戻るんだ。}I am returning to the club as their captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのためには誰よりも誰よりも強くなくちゃいけない。}This means I must get stronger than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなにXX休んでなんか要られないわ。}A break is the least what I need now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{半年ぐらい我慢できないの？}Can't you endure it for half a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー止めなさい！\Nーお！}- Stop it!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボール返してよ！}Give the ball back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…！}Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり！}Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫か？}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{放っといてよ！}Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたなんかにバレーのこと分かるもんか？}You understand nothing about volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{今度はダムの建設だ。}This time we're constructing a dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{山の中だから、今までよりXX帰XXだろう。}It's near the mountains so I won't be going home for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{お父さんがいない間、お母さんにあんまり心配をかけないよにな。}Don't make your mom worry too much when I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーの練習なんかやめるんだぞ？}You'll give up that volleyball thing, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{いやよ。}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{何？}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう大丈夫よ。ほら。}It healed already. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり。}Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{未だ分からんのか？}Do you still not get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{医者はバレーをやっちゃいけないと言っただろ？}The doctor told you to stop, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいな？}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かったな？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{だれががお医者さんXXに言うように頼んだのを知ってるは。}I realized who has asked the doctor for such a diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしを憎んでるだれがさんが。}It's a certain someone who hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{何てことを言うんだ？}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうなのよ。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{この人はあたしを憎いのよ。}This woman hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{だから、あたしからこの人はバレーを取り上げ落としてるんだわ。}That's why she tries to make me part with volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{お母さんに向かってお前は…}How dare you speak like that to your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{何よ！}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんな人はあたしのお母さんじゃないわよ。}This woman isn't my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしのお母さんはね…}My mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{もっとやさしく、心の美しい人だわ。}…was nicer and had a gentle heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり！}Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{お待ちなさい！}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{お前の右手は…}Your right hand's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなた！}Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{今の母さんにくられて…}She fights with her current mom so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:16:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなXXになんてなくなったお母さんはことが尚更いい人を思えるのね。}She sees her to be inferior to the biological mother, who has passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーは半年も休まなければいけない。}She won't settle for taking a six months long break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{その上お母さんとうまくいかない。}Plus she fights with her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くんに話を聞いたとき…}When I talked with her…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕はどう答えていた分からなくてね。}I didn't really know what to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、もう泣くの止せよ。}Come on, stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{人に見られたら、変に思われずね。}If people saw us, they'd jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいの。}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}I just can't take it any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなやけをお越し駄目だよ。}Don't feel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{冷静に成るんだ。ね、泉くん？}Stay calm, okay, Izumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね？}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん。}Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、泉くん。}Hey, Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・かれし)じなかったのね。}I misjudged you back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、もう一度泉さんと話してましょうよ。}Hey, let's talk to her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり。}Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたは…}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{なによ？何だって言うのよ？}What? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{学校行くのは嫌なったの。}I don't feel like going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{それだけよ。放っといてよ、ね。}That's it. Leave me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{学校止めて、東京へ行くなんて、そんなことは絶対にいけません。}I can't let you quit the school and go to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:16:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{許しませんよ。}I won't forgive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、ゆり。}Hey, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{お願いだから、あたしの言うことを聞いて。}Please, listen to what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{いやよ！}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたの言うことなんか聞きたくないんだったら。}I won't listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしなんかいなくなった方があんたもいいんでしょう？}You'd be better off if I wasn't here, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー分かってるわよ。\Nーゆり！}- I know that—\N- Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうせあたしなんか…どうなったて構わないでしょう。}You don't care what happens to me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり！}Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり。}Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーのできる君達は嫉ましかったんだろう。}She was jealous of you, who could play volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{それであんなことまでして、皆を裏切って、今泉くんはどれほど辛いおもいをしてるか。}That's why she did it all and betrayed you\h– she wanted you to feel the pain too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{小母さん！}Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{小母さん。}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、一ノ瀬さん。}Ah, Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{何か？}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{私…}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆりと嫌になって、つい…}…argued with Yuri…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうしたら、いきなり家から飛び出して…}…and all of the sudden, she fled home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは探していきます。}We'll look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{頼むよ。}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{小母さん。}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしははっきり言えばよかったんです。}I should have told her clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、どうしても言えなくて…}But I just couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{小母さん、何をですか？}What do you mean, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん。}Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さんから聞いた。}We heard it from Tsutomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{手首の具合は悪いなんて…知らなかったわ。}We had no idea about your wrist condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうして話してくれなかったの？}Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{話して何、何の?}What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{同情何かしてほしくないわ。}I don't want your sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{別に同情なんかしないわ。}We don't intend to be sympathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{手首が悪いじゃ、バレーを止めれX仕方ないじゃないの。そうじゃない？}Your wrist is no good. You quit the volleyball club and it can't be helped. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{だからあなた陸上部で入ったんでしょう？}That's why you entered the track and field club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{だったら、陸上部で一所懸命にやればいいじゃないの？}Then why don't you try your earnest in your new club?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{それがどうしてできないの？}Why can't you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、そうっか。}Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーでは四天王と言われてほど有名だった。}In the volleyball club, you had your Big Four fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{それが陸上部に入れば、一からやり直し。}But in the new club you'd start from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部の時のように有名に成るかどうか、不安なんでしょう。}You were anxious whether you could repeat this success.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{だからやる気がないのね。}This is why you had no motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{違うわ！}That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーをできない間…せめて陸上部に入った一所懸命やろうとしたわ。}When I found out I couldn't play the volleyball, I wanted to give the track and field club my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、どうしてもバレーのことも忘れられなくて。}But I couldn't forget about the volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あなたは陸上部選んだのは—}But you chose the track and field club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{走り自身があったからでしょう。}You were confident you could run well, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{(所が)陸上部に入ってやってみると思ったより苦しい。}However, when you joined, it turned out to be more demanding than you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{それを自身無くした。}So your motivation dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{だらしが無いのね。}What a bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん！}Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、どうかしたの？}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{酷い言い方するのね、あなたって—}You're pretty rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{だってその通りでしょう？}But I'm right, am I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{天井のよ。あなたの考え方は。}Your way of thinking is naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{そこまで言われて、黙っていられないわ。}If you go further, I won't keep silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうするって言うの?}What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしと競争でもしてみる？}How about we compete right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あなたに勝てるかしら。}I wonder if you can win, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは百メートル十三秒よ。}My time for 100 meters is 13 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっとむりじゃない？}Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けないわ。}I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたなんかに負けるもんか。}I won't lose to the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{やりましょうよ。}Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう。}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ。}Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{一番のこの松の木前でしましょう。}The first to circle that tree and returns, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょうど百メートルぐらいよ。}It's right about 100 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん、スターとお願い。}Midori-san, please give us a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいわ。}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{位置について。}Take positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんに自身をつけさせるため、鮎原さんは負けるつもりなのかしら？}I wonder if Ayuhara-san plans to lose on purpose to help Izumi-san regain her confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けないわ。}I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{絶対勝つ。}I will surely win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{よい！}Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか。}I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けないわ。}I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか！}I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けられないわ！}I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか！}I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか…！}I won't lose…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんかぁ！}I won't lose…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さんの勝ちだ。}Winner is Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{わざと負けるなんて…やっぱり鮎原さんのらしくないもんね。}As expected, losing on purpose isn't Ayuhara-san's style.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしの勝ちね。}Looks like I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{どんなに苦しくても…}No matter how hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{どんなに辛くても…}No matter how harsh…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{自分の全力を(XXX・出すXXX素敵)ね。}Doing something with all your might feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはスポーツをする人の気持ちなのね。}It's the sensation of sportsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはXXXスポーツをする資格はないわ。}People using traps aren't entitled to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{お母さんのことにしても、あなたはお母さんのやさしい気持ちを分かると努力しないじゃないの。}Even though your mom cares about you, you don't understand her feelings and fight her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{お母さんの気持ちも分からない。}You fight with your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{スポーツをする心も分からない。}You don't get sportsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな人は…バレーだって、陸上だって…皆やめてしまいはいいのよ。}A person like you has no business with both volleyball and track and field clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ。行きましょう。}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん！}Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし…}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{走るわ！}…will keep running.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{止めないわ！}I won't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん。}Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん。}Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{君のこの手首はね…}It's about your wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{動脈閉塞症で、これ以上バレーを続けると、君の手首は…まったく駄目に成っちゃうんだ。}You're suffering from arterial occlusion. If you continue volleyball, your wrist will give out completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう言うことなの？}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう二度とバレーはできないんだ。}You can't do volleyball ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{医者ははっきりそう言ったんだけど。}The doctor has made himself clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{お母さんは君にそこまでは言えなかったんだよ。}But your mom couldn't tell it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{だから、半年ぐらい休めばと言うことにして、}Instead, she softened it and told you to stop for half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{君にバレーを何とかして諦めさせをおとしなんだよ。}She planned to talk you out of it somehow during that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん。}Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{お母さん。}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{お母さん！}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.18,0:23:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボールを強く打ったりしなければ大丈夫よ。}If you don't hit the ball hard, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{最初からはっきり言えばよかったんだけど。}I should have told you the truth from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう二度とバレーはできないだなんて…どうしても言えなかったのよ。}But I was unable to tell you to give up the volleyball forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{お母さん。}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.67,0:23:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり。}Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし…}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってみる。}…will try.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{陸上部でやってみるわ。}I'll do my best in the track and field club.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーに全力でぶつかったと同じよ。}I'll put in the same strength I put into volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.52,0:23:54.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{念願の全国大会初出場は成った。}The first match in All-Japan Tournament draws near.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:56.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{「君達には優勝する実力がある。」}"You have what it takes to win."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:23:58.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{…と本郷コーチは保証する。}— professor Hongou encourages the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:02.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{富士見学園チームはXXなって、東京に向かった。}The Fujimi Academy team goes to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:03.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{懐かしい東京。}The nostalgic Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.82,0:24:06.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{こずえはXX明法学園を訪れた。}Kozue visits the Meihou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.60,0:24:11.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{だが、明法の体育館で練習中の福岡中学を見て、XX。}In the Meihou's gym, she meets powerful peers from Fukuoka Middle School in the middle of practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:15.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{中学生には及びもつかないレシーブを知っている戦士がいる。}Some of them know a receive technique way above middle schoolers level.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.27,0:24:18.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{こずえの自身は俄に崩れかかる。}Kozue's confidence quickly collapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.07,0:24:21.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
